reviews.text: The signature 招牌清汤牛腩河粉 is tasty but be careful when you order upside as it could either mean more hor fan or more beef. The beef is tasty and soup is nice. Price wise is a bit on the high side but still affordable I guess.
Ordered the upsizes of 牛腩粿条汤 thinking of more meat. In return only 10% are meat and 90% noodle. 2 pieces of the meat are pure fat which are very wrong for 牛腩. Really disappointed. DO NOT RECOMMEND.
